<ab facs="#facs_139_r2l10">lxxx ſchok <expan>Beheymiſch<ex>er</ex></expan> groſʒ . hanſen Ortlieb j<hi rend="sup">C</hi> ſchok </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_139_r2l11"><expan>Beheẏmiſch<ex>er</ex></expan> gröſʒ xxxix vngeriſch vnd xviij Reyniſch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_139_r2l12">guldlein . heincʒen volknant / j<hi rend="sup">C</hi> vnd iiij ſchok </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_139_r2l13"><expan>Beheymiſch<ex>er</ex></expan> groſʒ . Vnd dem Markart Scheffein dreẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_139_r2l14">mark vnd iij lot <expan>v<ex>er</ex>gults</expan> <expan>ſilb<ex>er</ex>s</expan> . cʒwu mark mẏnder </ab>
